a `` front door'' for invasion, and such weapons as shoulder-fired missiles could threaten all Israeli air strips. <PERSON> Netanyahu </PERSON> said the uprising should be ended, followed by a `` cooling-off period'' and an autonomy plan that gives <LOCATION> Israel </LOCATION> maximum security and the Arab residents minimum interference.
